  "comment": "WELL PANEL X is the ideal addition to any rental package, offering an easily deployed and controlled fixture with high CRI that renders skin tones beautifully and make this panel an excellent key light. A higher quantity of smaller LEDs in this design ensures better color mixing than ever before. Up to 18 hours of battery life from a fixture engineered to meet the needs of lighting professionals working in environments where quick setup and flexibility are crucial. Roll into any production, indoors or out, with a fully-realized road-worthy four-unit kit with built-in charging capability.",
